item.title: Just Enough Reverse Engineering
item.description: The 2nd meetup will be later today. The theme for the meetup is Reverse Engineering and it will start with a presentation to get you started in this exciting field. The presentation will be recorded and will be added to the site, but for now you can already download the slide deck for this meetup here!
